      <title>利洁时开始就 60 亿英镑家庭护理资产出售进行谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/reckitt-said-to-start-talks-on-6-billion-homecare-assets-sale</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，利洁时集团已开始与一些潜在的买家就其家庭护理资产进行初步洽谈，交易价值可能超过 60 亿英镑（79 亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/reckitt-said-to-start-talks-on-6-billion-homecare-assets-sale</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 17:10:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
